        {
            "id": 6434251,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 英特爾(INTC-US)大漲5.16%，報86.8美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)截至台北時間27日21:59股價上漲4.26美元，報86.80美元，漲幅5.16%，成交量49,715,190（股），盤中最高價86.80美元、最低價82.79美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.01%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.03%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.15%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.83%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+20.5%</li> <li>近 1 月：+87.17%</li> <li>近 3 月：+94.26%</li> <li>近 6 月：+115.62%</li> <li>今年以來：+123.69%</li></ul></section></main>",
